        <h1 class="proj-title">What 7 Years of Design<br>Gave Me as a PM</h1>
        <p class="proj-sub">Not a list of soft skills. The specific instincts a design background builds, where they're genuinely useful in product work, and the one habit I had to unlearn completely.</p>
